    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Binary ops between DataFrame of time series and a single time series has been special-cased to go column-by-column. This is some serious legacy stuff from pandas 0.1 and should probably receive a deprecation message in 0.10, to get users to change their code to use one of the explicit functions\n"
